In plain English:

  * Free to use, modify, redistribute, including commercially.
  * Credit CY Future when you publish work that builds on this.
  * If you publish derivatives, please keep them open.
  * Don't weaponize this against systems you don't have permission to test.
  * No warranty; pilot-stage; do not deploy as your only defense in
    safety-critical contexts.
  * Beyond the above, do whatever helps the field.
